commitResults.messageBody:
Currently, we have no storage for reviews.

JsonAdaptedStall will have to store reviews in the storage. Currently,
there is no JsonAdaptedReview class so we will use JsonAdaptedStall as
a proxy for this JsonAdaptedReview class.

Let's
- add reviews to stall storage
- fix up tests

Currently, when a Stall is renamed, the corresponding review do not get
renamed to match the name of the stall. This behavior is considered to
be a bug.

Let's
1. Update StallBuilder to rename the reviews when building
2. Update SEditCommand::createEditedStall to rename the reviews when
building
